import { formatCurrency } from "../helpers/number-helper" import { useHistory } from "react-router-dom" const OrderItem = ({ order }) => { const history = useHistory() return (
history.push("/order/" + order.orderId)} > View Order
{order.orderId}
{order.shopName}
{order.status}
{formatCurrency(order.totalPrice)}
) } export default OrderItem
